在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-adds-more-us-dates-to-the-midwest-princess-tour-buy-tickets-3775795">一系列美国约会</a>之后完成。</p><p>请参阅<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-announces-anniversary-vinyl-for-rise-fall-midwest-princess-3781700" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处的</a>演出的完整列表，并<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fchappell-roan-tickets%2Fartist%2F2397430" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a><a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fchappell-roan-tickets%2Fartist%2F5237263" target="_blank" rel="noopener">找到</a>英国和欧洲节目的剩余门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-reacts-as-fans-say-harris-walz-campaign-merch-looks-like-hers-3782125">Chappell Roan邮报的反应正如粉丝们说，Harris-Walz竞选商品看起来像她</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现。</p> ;
